---
title: Teriyaki-Glazed Pork Rissoles with Garlic Rice & Asian Sesame Slaw
description: The humble rissole gets a whole new look and taste with this easy glazed version. A crisp and colourful slaw on the side is the perfect accompaniment to this meal that will make you rethink the classics!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-glazed-pork-rissoles-a61d26c5.jpg
